liteTabs is a lightweight tab plugin for jQuery.

Options:
borders : false,        // draw borders around tabs
boxed : false,          // draw bordered box around tab container
fadeIn : false,         // fade in tab contents
height : 'auto',        // set height
hideHash : false,       // hide the url hash (not recommended)
rounded : false,        // rounded corners
selectedTab : 1,        // initially selected tab
width : 500             // set width